===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|pere|lang=ang}}, common North and West Germanic, from {{etyl|VL.|en}} {{term/t|la|*pira}}, originally the plural of {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|pirum|lang=la}} but reconstrued as a feminine singular.

